long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This a simple yet useful Extension for getting Leetcode video solutions from youtube just with one click.
The extension automatically detects on which problem number you are on and grabs you the solution for the particular problem.
